dcterms:description: The hourly time series data used to train the networks is available for Ahmedabad airport specifically, from 2010 to 2017. The weather condition parameters in the data include temperature, wind speed, pressure, and humidity.
dcterms:title: Indian weather pattern

dcterms:description: This dataset includes multiple weather condition parameters like humidity, pressure, temperature, wind speed, and wind direction for different cities. Data for only those cities have been considered where rainfall occurs more often and in measurable amounts.
dcterms:title: Historical Hourly Weather Data 2012-2017
